The paper deals with communication networks and their energy efficiency, which are topics typically covered in the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. The use of distributed relaying schemes and cooperative communication also suggests a possible fit with the Multimedia (cs.MM) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
